    "Linene confirms the gang's raids are choking Phandalin's trade through Ashfall Watch."
  ],
  "journal": [
    "Your soldier's opening leaves you with a live look at how hard Neverwinter is leaning on thin patrol lines and tired veterans to protect the road south.",
